ğŸ§  What Makes This Project Strong (Beyond CRUD)

Ink demonstrates how real applications are built, not just how CRUD works.
This project includes:

JWT-based authentication flow used in production systems
Ownership-based authorization (only authors can edit their blogs)
Shared schema validation between frontend and backend
Edge-deployed backend for low latency
Versioned API design (/api/v1)
Clear separation of frontend, backend, and shared logic
Scalable structure ready for new features


